August 24

Open Tournament at Hiit Hard Strength

The VABL – Open Tournament at Hiit Hard Strength and Conditioning is set to be a compelling boxing event, where a diverse mix of fighters—from promising newcomers to experienced competitors—will step into the ring. Hosted in a facility known for its rigorous training environment, this tournament offers a great opportunity for athletes to showcase their skills and determination. The event is part of the Virginia Amateur Boxing League and promises to deliver solid, competitive bouts that highlight the dedication and talent within the local boxing community.
